# String.matches — full-string regex match, INT==JS==JVM

Guard for the JS-lane `matches` dispatch (added for tkv2-forms pattern
validators): Scala semantics = the WHOLE string must match.

```scalascript
println("abc@x.io".matches("[^@]+@[^@]+"))
println("nope".matches("[^@]+@[^@]+"))
println("12345".matches("[0-9]{5}"))
println("123".matches("[0-9]{5}"))
```
